text.tspan: We are pleased to offer you acceptance into our CodeLabs internship program.
In the CodeLabs program, you will be assigned to work on a project which we have
mutually agreed upon with between 1-5 other students. You will recieve day-to-day
mentorship by a volunteer from the technology industry, however your work will
ultimately be supervised by a CodeDay employee:
Skip-level supervisor: Tyler Menezes (Executive Director, CodeDay)
This is unpaid, and does not constitute an employment relationship.
